OL,3,CWelsh teenagers up for BAFTA awards
OL,4,Cfor video games creation
OL,6,FTwo teenagers from Wales are being
OL,7,Frecognised by BAFTA for their work in
OL,8,Fcreating video games.
OL,10,FJack Rafferty, 17, from Cowbridge and
OL,11,FRobert Russin, 15, from Penarth are
OL,12,Ffinalists in the BAFTA Young Game
OL,13,FDesigners.
OL,15,FThe awards champion the work of
OL,16,Fyoungsters aged between 12-18 with a
OL,17,Fceremony taking place on 27 June.
