OL,6,FBAFTA Young Game Designers work with
OL,7,Fschools across the UK to develop the
OL,8,Fskills of children who are interested
OL,9,Fin games.
OL,11,FJack's game, Voidside, is a high-
OL,12,Foctane survival mission set in a
OL,13,Fseries of locations 'pulled out of
OL,14,Ftime', following a mysterious event
OL,15,Fknown as 'the shattering'.
OL,17,FThe 17-year-old said: "I learnt a lot;
OL,18,Ffrom furthering my programming
OL,19,Fknowledge to learning how to release a
OL,20,Fgame on steam.
