OL,6,F"Colour theory played a big part in
OL,7,Fhow I designed Voidside's levels, and
OL,8,Fcreating these levels taught me about
OL,9,Fgame lighting, level design and more."
OL,11,FJack added that he's hoping to develop
OL,12,Fthe game into a full-blown sequel in
OL,13,Fthe future, with "better enemy AI,
OL,14,Fbetter level design, a story mode and
OL,15,Fmuch more!"
OL,17,FRobert's game which is called clim3r
OL,18,Fis a 2D platformer featuring a player
OL,19,Fcharacter with three arms.
