OL,6,FThe user has to understand the
OL,7,Fprinciples of gravity and momentum to
OL,8,Fmove the main character across gaps
OL,9,Fand to allow them to climb effectively.
OL,11,FOn the game's development, Robert
OL,12,Fsaid: "I had to spend lots of time on
OL,13,Fthe character's body, which is
OL,14,Fentirely physics based and simulated
OL,15,Fwith joints and bones, making it run
OL,16,Fas smoothly as possible on different
OL,17,Fcomputers."
