OL,3,CWelsh teenagers up for BAFTA awards
OL,4,Cfor video games creation
OL,6,FThis year's finalists have been
OL,7,Fshortlisted for two awards. The YGD
OL,8,FGame Concept Award rewards the most
OL,9,Foriginal and best thought-out game
OL,10,Fidea, while the YGD Game Making Award
OL,11,Fgoes to the most impressive use of
OL,12,Fcoding skills on a freely available
OL,13,Fsoftware, to create a prototype game.
OL,15,FBoth awards are split into two age
OL,16,Fcategories: 10-14 years and 15-18
OL,17,Fyears.
